videoSnippet.title: What Happens When 1991 Chessmaster Faces Stockfish 14 NNUE
videoSnippet.description:
Read up on NNUE Stockfish here https://www.chess.com/blog/the_real_greco/evolution-of-a-chess-fish-what-is-nnue-anyway#:~:text=What%20does%20NNUE%20stand%20for,NNUE%20is%20wordplay%20in%20Japanese.

Watch entire Bobby Fischer saga here! https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0A8-8M8fb04&list=PLDnx7w_xuguENa5LgFG7Gi8aYRVVnXxFE

Have a great day :)

Stockfish 14 + NNUE vs Chessmaster 2000
Friendly Game
C90 Ruy Lopez, closed (with ...d6)

1.e4 e5 2.Nf3 Nc6 3.Bb5 a6 4.Ba4 Nf6 5.O-O Be7 6.Re1 b5 7.Bb3 d6 8.c3 O-O 9.a4 Bg4 10.h3 bxa4 11.Bxa4 Bxf3 12.Qxf3 Na5 13.b4 Nc4 14.Bc6 Rb8 15.d3 Rb6 16.Ba4 d5 17.dxc4 dxe4 18.Qe3 Qa8 19.c5 Rbb8 20.Bc2 Rfd8 21.Nd2 Nd5 22.Qxe4 Nxc3 23.Qxh7+ Kf8 24.Qh8#
